channel.title: Problem with my vps finding PATHS in Java
channel.description:
Well right after I got my vps, eclipse, and everything ran very smoothly, but I changed sources and now when I try to run eclipse, cannot find the path specified, even when i try to run my server, it says it cant find the path specified. I have been trying to fix this for about 3 hours, and I am just getting very frustrated. If anyone could help I would greatly appreciate it, and benefits could be involved depending on what you can do. My Skype is: jacob.doyle58
Thanks, ~Jacob
